## 9ï¸âƒ£ Common mistakes freshers make ğŸš«

1. âŒ Using nested loops (O(nÂ²))
2. âŒ Not checking length first
3. âŒ Confusing rotation with permutation
4. âŒ Checking only one shift
5. âŒ Case mismatch (`"Abc"` vs `"abc"`)

